Interface IEdgeInfo


  • public interface IEdgeInfo
    A class that holds all information associated with an edge.

      • getId

        Object getId()
        Gets the unique ID of the associated edge.
        Returns:
        the ID of the associated edge
        See Also:
        MultiPageLayoutResult.getEdgeInfo(Edge), IElementInfoManager.getEdgeInfo(Edge)

      • getRepresentedEdge

        Edge getRepresentedEdge()
        Gets the original edge associated with this IEdgeInfo.

        More precisely, for edges of type EdgeType.CONNECTOR, this method returns the edge of the input graph that was split by the connector edge. Otherwise, it returns null.

        Returns:
        the original edge if the type of the edge is EdgeType.CONNECTOR, null otherwise
        See Also:
        EdgeType.CONNECTOR
